      "properties": {"text": ""},
      "widgets_values": [
        "=== EXPRESSION INPAINT · dnd3 ===\n\nMISMO CHECKPOINT + 3 LoRAs que el sprite base → consistencia total\nUSA FaceDetailer (Impact Pack) → detecta la cara automáticamente, sin máscara manual.\nRequiere: bbox/face_yolov8n.pt → ComfyUI/models/ultralytics/bbox/\nDescarga: https://huggingface.co/Bingsu/adetailer/resolve/main/face_yolov8n.pt\nO desde Manager → Install Models → busca face_yolov8n\n\n──── USO ────\n1. Subí el portrait base a ComfyUI/input/\n2. Seleccionalo en el nodo LoadImage\n3. Cambiá el positivo (tras el BREAK) según la expresión deseada\n4. Queue Prompt\n\n──── EXPRESIONES — cambiar sólo el positivo (tras el BREAK) ────\n  ANGRY:      clenched teeth, furrowed brows, wide bloodshot eyes, battle fury, veins on forehead\n  SCARED:     wide terrified eyes, cold sweat, pale skin, trembling lips, horror expression\n  DETERMINED: sharp focused eyes, calm intensity, set jaw, unwavering fierce gaze\n  SMUG:       half-lidded eyes, twisted smirk, condescending gaze, sinister confidence\n  SAD:        tears streaming, downcast eyes, trembling chin, grief expression\n  SURPRISED:  wide open eyes, raised brows, open mouth shock, jaw drop\n  NEUTRAL:    calm composed face, relaxed expression, neutral gaze\n\n──── DENOISE GUIDE (FaceDetailer) ────\n  0.35 → muy sutil (casi invisible)\n  0.50 → sweet spot (cambia expresión, mantiene identidad)  ← DEFAULT\n  0.65 → agresivo (más cambio, riesgo de perder identidad)\n  0.80 → máximo (casi re-genera la cara completa)"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    }
